Request deletion of all data stored by “GatekeeperAI”
If you want us to delete all data that Your App Name has stored from your Facebook login (such as your name, email address, and any other profile information received from Facebook), please send us a request using one of the following methods:
	•	Email: support@yourdomain.com
	•	Subject: Facebook Data Deletion Request – GatekeeperAI
In your message, please include:
	•	Your full name
	•	The email address associated with your Facebook account
	•	(Optional) Your Facebook User ID, if known
